name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: ipc.[port_number].weighted-cost.lockexclusive
description:
The weight multiplier to apply to the time spent in the
    processing phase which holds an exclusive (write) lock.
    This property applies to WeightedTimeCostProvider.

name: hadoop.zk.num-retries
description: Number of tries to connect to ZooKeeper.

name: fs.getspaceused.jitterMillis
description: fs space usage statistics refresh jitter in msec.

name: dfs.disk.balancer.max.disk.throughputInMBperSec
description:
Maximum disk bandwidth used by diskbalancer
      during read from a source disk. The unit is MB/sec.
